data.description: Welcome to 16922 Turin Ridge, a meticulously maintained and beautifully presented home located in the coveted Sonoma Mesa community. This stunning residence exudes luxury from the moment you arrive, with its striking brick and stone facade and manicured curb appeal enhanced by mature landscaping. Situated on one of the largest home sites in the neighborhood, this property offers an unparalleled blend of charm, sophistication, and livability, epitomizing the essence of luxury living. Step inside through the grand 8-foot door and be greeted by the impressive foyer, where the soaring 18-foot ceilings and impeccable attention to detail in the beautiful finishes immediately captivate your attention. The open concept design flawlessly combines style and functionality, creating a seamless flow throughout the home. The gourmet kitchen is a true chef's dream, boasting luxurious 42-inch cabinets, design-select granite countertops and backsplash, stainless steel appliances, and an expansive island that overlooks the inviting living room. Here, a stunning stone fireplace adds warmth and character, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxation and entertainment. The main level of the home features a spacious primary bedroom that offers breathtaking views, a spa-like master bath for indulgent self-care, and a large closet that caters to all your storage needs. Additionally, a convenient secondary guest bedroom is located on this level, providing privacy and comfort for your guests. As you ascend the lovely wrought iron and wood stairwell to the second level, you'll discover a versatile game room, perfect for unwinding and spending quality time with loved ones. Adjacent to the game room, a media room awaits, providing an ideal space for hosting watch parties and enjoying your favorite movies or sports teams. The second level also boasts three additional bedrooms, with one of them enjoying the luxury of its own private bathroom. For outdoor enthusiasts, the extended covered patio beckons you to step outside and immerse yourself in the breathtaking views of the gorgeous surrounding hills. Whether it's a quiet moment of relaxation or a gathering of friends and family, this outdoor haven is the perfect spot to unwind and create lasting memories. Not only is this home a private sanctuary, but it also benefits from a prime location, with a wide selection of eateries, shopping and entertainment options nearby. Experience the epitome of luxury living in this meticulously crafted home that effortlessly combines elegance, comfort, and convenience.
